{"tid":1840623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民大罷工］記住罷工係為自己 為家人 為香港","createTime":"2020-01-25T02:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T23:59:32.000Z","uid":18577,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ebede4ec2fb4290c83c0fa85a885a3b928d996d0","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"上次1124區議會選舉個陣我重未生<br />\n所以好慶幸去到投票..更開心係見到選舉結果證明我哋先係主流民意<br />\n而民意從來都無逆轉過<br />\n<br />\n去到依刻生咗連豬女出黎（佢係豬年出世呀）<br />\n日日係屋企攬住個女睇武漢肺炎嘅新聞<br />\n真係成日都驚到好想喊<br />\n我染病唔緊要呀 最驚係個女有咩事<br />\n我真係唔知香港人做錯d乜要陪依班中國人去死<br />\n更加唔明點解個死仆街政府到依刻都唔封關唔停高鐵<br />\n<br />\n而呀媽我可以做嘅除咗日日係連登開post<br />\n重有就係日日炸屋企人gp<br />\n同藍絲講港共政府幾垃圾幾痴線咁推香港人去死<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n去到年初一<br />\n希望各位連登巴絲應承我<br />\n去拜年嘅時候<br />\n一定一定要數臭依個政府<br />\n重有一定要同佢哋宣傳罷工<br />\n要撐醫護罷工嘅最好方法係大家一齊同佢哋罷<br />\n因為罷工完完全全係為咗你自己 你屋企人 同埋整個香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天佑香港</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9945c422d597cc6e01a660a5101cfc5ab6cbb0bb","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8545a92eb18a6218746415b202cf67c433143d7","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da945b8038c590ab07d0cdca83d7d9df49c3cb0e","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75963ee1864f627c0b2ab3e3e2fb778d25d7e1f7","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7700aa6d3dc3858c457ba23ccc8f848f87dcd1","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0f31b06d916a4ff654a5ad6ce9c2ff77f38c78","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbcba542f5fb877a556298152314b254997c614","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39488bc821571e7ef9ecb7389e80cbe257c2831a","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9ef30598fe40cba8dc567926923c249e78290a","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce14134d6abb10a7a5c859141fb180f823b03d0","tid":1840623,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=676f3a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知，唔使有太大道德包袱，因為政府把關不足先係根本問題，呢個民意調查話你地知市民撐你地！會尊重你地既決定"},{"pid":"fbc0558c7e08fa2f1dec4e1e4f3f1e4971065a39","tid":1840623,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"咁好嘅文都上唔到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上去] 罷工比返工救得更多嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6277db071372367d3f3f6c653df170dfd0b4d85","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce14134d6abb10a7a5c859141fb180f823b03d0","tid":1840623,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=676f3a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知，唔使有太大道德包袱，因為政府把關不足先係根本問題，呢個民意調查話你地知市民撐你地！會尊重你地既決定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a66c3601e3803ca82b2848389d61bd7d8d959e6","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbc0558c7e08fa2f1dec4e1e4f3f1e4971065a39","tid":1840623,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"咁好嘅文都上唔到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上去] 罷工比返工救得更多嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840117</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"614d776afc1665e69b11c60a49986d8b348ec2a9","tid":1840623,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"